# Logs
logs
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*

# Optional npm cache directory
.npm

# Optional eslint cache
.eslintcache

# macOS
.DS_Store

# Note: node_modules is intentionally NOT ignored here. 
# Because the auto-merge action relies on `@actions/core` and `@actions/github` 
# being present at runtime, and we haven't set up a build step (like `ncc`) to bundle them, 
# `node_modules` must be committed to the repository for the action to work on GitHub.
